com.tianscar.javasound.midi.spi

Interface SoundbankResourceReader

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JDKSoundbankResourceReader

    public interface SoundbankResourceReader
    A SoundbankResourceReader supplies soundbank resource-reading services. Concrete subclasses of SoundbankReader parse a given soundbank resource, producing a Soundbank object that can be loaded into a Synthesizer.

                                 throws javax.sound.midi.InvalidMidiDataException,
                                        java.io.IOException
        Obtains a soundbank object from the resource provided.
        Parameters:
        resourceLoader - the ClassLoader to load resource
        name - resource name representing the soundbank.
        Returns:
        soundbank object
        Throws:
        javax.sound.midi.InvalidMidiDataException - if the resource does not point to valid MIDI soundbank data recognized by this soundbank reader
        java.io.IOException - if an I/O error occurs
